Package: badgen
Type: Package
Title: Fast and Simple Badge Generator
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Jeroen", "Ooms", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jeroenooms@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4035-0289"))
Description: Bindings to 'badgen' <https://www.npmjs.com/package/badgen> to
    generate beautiful 'svg' badges in R without internet access. Images can
    be converted to 'png' using the 'rsvg' package as shown in examples.
